txt.en: Bring the claw of Kurthár to Agátur
Collect the claw of Kurthár for Agátur
Kurthár and cave-beasts can be found in Máttugard.\n\nYou should defeat cave-beasts.
Agátur can be found at Steepset in Máttugard.\n\nYou should bring the claw of Kurthár to Agátur.
'Oh ho! This is the claw of Kurthár indeed! Many at Steepset will rejoice to see this beast no more when travelling through Máttugard. You have done a good deed, [placeholder].'

'Hmm, have you seen the beast, [placeholder]? Bah, I speak of Kurthár, the mighty cave-beast! Kurthár is a terrible menace in Máttugard. The beast has ransacked multiple supply carts and must be stopped! Find Kurthár and bring me its claw. Only then shall I rest easily.'
Agátur the Boastful asks you to seek out Kurthár, a terrible cave-beast found in Máttugard.
